    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/b4d02d64f65126d9073a075e3128d9db.avif?t=1760467937\" width=611 height=213 /></span><br>在《Kitty Rhythm Tower Defense》中，小猫咪们已经准备好将任何派对变成一场成功！这款游戏结合了塔防策略与音乐节奏，挑战你布置音乐塔，确保所有小老鼠都开心。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/f71d50138ccaddad3df1fd6e31fa0a0c.poster.avif?t=1760467937\" width=610 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/f71d50138ccaddad3df1fd6e31fa0a0c.webm?t=1760467937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/f71d50138ccaddad3df1fd6e31fa0a0c.mp4?t=1760467937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/0668e26680c2ee6b085a03544a091376.avif?t=1760467937\" width=611 height=130 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/7ac426e220afeef7075441db8b6029ab.poster.avif?t=1760467937\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/7ac426e220afeef7075441db8b6029ab.webm?t=1760467937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/7ac426e220afeef7075441db8b6029ab.mp4?t=1760467937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每只小猫都是一座塔，演奏一种乐器，它们的动作与音乐的节拍同步。随着游戏的进行，你必须雇佣新的音乐家，确保每个人都能听到你的音乐！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/6a07dbb18cdadc258782d021a0f9474f.avif?t=1760467937\" width=611 height=130 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/234751328cfcce40eed3949bee48aa4a.poster.avif?t=1760467937\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/234751328cfcce40eed3949bee48aa4a.webm?t=1760467937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/234751328cfcce40eed3949bee48aa4a.mp4?t=1760467937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>作为指挥家，你必须协调音乐和小猫，让小老鼠们开心，并防止派对失去节奏。管理你的能量，避免小猫们筋疲力尽！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/8194b6ea0636ddac2eaa50e65920675b.avif?t=1760467937\" width=611 height=130 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/74507a2c299aeca66b8f0f7b138e9d27.avif?t=1760467937\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras_big/74507a2c299aeca66b8f0f7b138e9d27.avif?t=1760467937 width=800 height=392 /></span><br>随着游戏的进行，你可以升级你的塔，显著提升它们的音乐力量！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/df9e3a228a99b85dade6241c7c1ccedf.avif?t=1760467937\" width=611 height=131 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras/d5d40d1af88de1bd6fcb43c9ed96e15f.poster.avif?t=1760467937\" width=610 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213680/extras